Package: sondr
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Survey Data Management and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: CLESSN, Ellipse, CAPP
Maintainer: Hubert Cadieux <hubert.cadieux.1@ulaval.ca>
Description: Provides a collection of functions designed to streamline the process of cleaning, merging, and analyzing survey data.
    Offers tools to handle common tasks in survey data management such as dealing with missing values, recoding variables and merging completely different datasets as well as performing specific analytical procedures that are commonly used in survey data analysis.
